{"title":"走进发射场","authors":["纪学"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":7,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进发射场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么宽阔健硕的身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么高大威武的形象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽着戈壁滔滔雄风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶着漫天如火的骄阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观测仪是它明亮的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫星导弹是它腾飞的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那矫健的钢铁翎羽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪射灿烂的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然此刻没有呼啸响起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有云霞托起辉煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我分明看到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这沉默里隐藏的惊雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托起一个民族如花的期冀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长空里绚丽地开放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声里包容的烈火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有着怎样的力量"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}